  "sn14.38:1.1": "Saṃyutta Nikāya 14",
  "sn14.38:2.1": "4. Catutthavagga",
  "sn14.38:3.1": "38. Dutiyasamaṇabrāhmaṇasutta",
  "sn14.38:4.1": "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati.",
  "sn14.38:4.2": "“Catasso imā, bhikkhave, dhātuyo.",
  "sn14.38:4.3": "Katamā catasso?",
  "sn14.38:4.4": "Pathavīdhātu, āpodhātu, tejodhātu, vāyodhātu.",
  "sn14.38:4.5": "Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā imāsaṃ catunnaṃ dhātūnaṃ samudayañca atthaṅgamañca assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ nappajānanti … pe …",
  "sn14.38:4.6": "(vitthāretabbaṃ) pajānanti … pe …",
  "sn14.38:4.7": "sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharantī”ti.",
  "sn14.38:5.1": "Navamaṃ."
}